Guess what we have been growing ❤️! We have only grown a few so far but each one is so precious and delicious.

Wow! I know the Harper family is late to the game but Wakanda Forever was incredible! I laughed, was surprised, cried, and was spiritually lifted up by some of the most beautiful scenes. I was particularly moved by the scenes in 🇭🇹 Haiti ❤️.This movie was so moving and helped me to remember that when there is loss and grief, their spirit stays with you forever. During the mourning, there can be beauty in their presence. It reminded me of worship, when I can imagine me holding Momma’s hand 🥰. @marvelstudios
